<div><head>《昕天論》</head>
<p>
<seg xml:id="CH2d1664_CHANT_001-1a.1"><pb xml:id="CH2d1664_CHANT_001-1a" ed="CHANT" n="001-1a"/><lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2d1664_CHANT_001-1a.2">昕天論<lb/></seg>
</p>
<p>
<seg xml:id="CH2d1664_CHANT_001-1a.3">若使天裏地如卵含雞地，<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2d1664_CHANT_001-1a.4">何所倚立而自安？<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2d1664_CHANT_001-1a.5">固若有四維柱石，<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2d1664_CHANT_001-1a.6">則天之運轉，<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2d1664_CHANT_001-1a.7">將以相官。<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2d1664_CHANT_001-1a.8">使無四維，<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2d1664_CHANT_001-1a.9">因水勢以浮，<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2d1664_CHANT_001-1a.10">則非立性也。<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2d1664_CHANT_001-1a.11">若天經行於水中，<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2d1664_CHANT_001-1a.12">則日月星辰之行，<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2d1664_CHANT_001-1a.13">將不得其性。<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2d1664_CHANT_001-1a.14">是以兩地之說，<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2d1664_CHANT_001-1a.15">下地則上地之根也，<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2d1664_CHANT_001-1a.16">天行乎兩地之間矣。<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2d1664_CHANT_001-1a.17">地形立於下，<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2d1664_CHANT_001-1a.18">天象運乎上，<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2d1664_CHANT_001-1a.19">人為靈蟲形最似天。<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2d1664_CHANT_001-1a.20">今人頤前多臨胸，<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2d1664_CHANT_001-1a.21">而項不能覆背近取諸身，<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2d1664_CHANT_001-1a.22">故知天之體南低入地，<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2d1664_CHANT_001-1a.23">北則偏高。<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2d1664_CHANT_001-1a.24">又冬至極低而天運近南，<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2d1664_CHANT_001-1a.25">故曰：<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2d1664_CHANT_001-1a.26">「去人遠而斗去人近。」<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2d1664_CHANT_001-1a.27">北天氣至，<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2d1664_CHANT_001-1a.28">故冰寒也。<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2d1664_CHANT_001-1a.29">夏至極起而。<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2d1664_CHANT_001-1a.30">天運近北，<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2d1664_CHANT_001-1a.31">故斗去人遠而日去人近，<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2d1664_CHANT_001-1a.32">南天氣至，<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2d1664_CHANT_001-1a.33">故蒸熱也。<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2d1664_CHANT_001-1a.34">極之立時，<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2d1664_CHANT_001-1a.35">日所行地中淺，<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2d1664_CHANT_001-1a.36">故夜短，<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2d1664_CHANT_001-1a.37">天去地高，<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2d1664_CHANT_001-1a.38">故晝長也。<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2d1664_CHANT_001-1a.39">極之低時，<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2d1664_CHANT_001-1a.40">日所行地中深，<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2d1664_CHANT_001-1a.41">故夜長，<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2d1664_CHANT_001-1a.42">天去地下淺，<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2d1664_CHANT_001-1a.43">故晝短也。<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2d1664_CHANT_001-1a.44">然則天寒依於渾，<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2d1664_CHANT_001-1a.45">夏俯於蓋也。<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2d1664_CHANT_001-1a.46">《太平御覽》卷二。<lb/></seg>
</p>
